Content:
blindFS 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14851] added cancellable heavy requests for LSP
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14837] implemented workspace-wide operations for LSP
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14818] fixed goto definition on variables in match guard
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14817] adjusted span of $it/$in to the first character of its scope
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14809] added inlay hints of types in assignments for LSP
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14848] fixed issue with variable names ending in duration suffix on the right side of a range
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14821] added a new 
``help pipe-and-redirect``
 command
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14847] fixed error propagation in export-env
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14841] added new operators 'has' and 'not-has'
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14804] added pipeline input support to 
``generate``
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14846] replaced skim with nucleo for faster completions
Tyarel8 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14845] made 'into datetime' a noop when input is already a datetime
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14835] updated Nu to 0.101.0 for workflow and pinned ubuntu-latest to 22.04 for riscv64gc build
ChrisDenton 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14832] used non-canonicalized paths in shell integrations
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14827] replaced icons in grid with devicons + color
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14819] finished removing terminal_size dependency
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14825] renamed/deprecated 'range' to 'slice'
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14765] removed required positional arguments from 'run-external' and 'exec'
